    <bodyTop>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Let’s talk business. When you study for a degree in business management at QMU you’ll gain a deep understanding of the nature and core functions of businesses. How do successful companies manage their resources? What’s the best way to make an organisation environmentally sustainable? What marks out a successful entrepreneur?</p>
<p>You can study a general business management degree or (after two years of general study) decide to focus your learning on the enterprise, finance or marketing elements of business management.</p>
<p>Are you bubbling with new business ideas? Are you prepared to do the hard work that will make them a success? Our BA (Hons) Business Management with Enterprise will help you finesse your entrepreneurial talents. In Years Three and Four, you can pick the modules best suited to your passion for enterprise. Year Four will probably be a particular highlight for you, as you’ll go on a live business placement and take the reins of an original, enterprise-focused piece of independent work. By the end of the course you’ll have broadened your career options and gained a solid foundation in the core principles of business management.</p>
<div class="mceNonEditable embeditem" data-embed-url="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8in6zDNyWEA" data-embed-height="346" data-embed-width="615" data-embed-constrain="false"><iframe width="615" height="346" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8in6zDNyWEA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" title="Marcel Strangmueller, BA (Hons) Business Management"></iframe></div>]]></Value>
    </bodyTop>
